      "key": "contribution.{57644AE6-7FFA-A231-8FE0-75-TX1000}.description",
      "source": "2005年秋開業したつくばエクスプレス線用の通勤車両。秋葉原から守谷までの直流区間を走行する。",
      "translation": "Commuter vehicle for the Tsukuba Express Line, which opened in autumn 2005. Operates on the DC section from Akihabara to Moriya."
