      "source": "2005年秋開業したつくばエクスプレス線用の近郊車両。つくばまで運行する交直流電車。",
      "translation": "Suburban vehicle for the Tsukuba Express Line, which opened in autumn 2005. An AC/DC electric train operating to Tsukuba."
